features for next releases:
---------------------------
	
	- Planned
		- selectable fields (mac, switch, port, ...)
		- custom fields;
		- translations (XML);
		- Independant VLAN management;
		- Create upgrade script for allowed groups and permissions;
	
	- Requests
		- custom groups
		- per-section permissions
		- Character support; (http://stackoverflow.com/questions/405684/php-mysql-with-encoding-problems)
		- Sorting of IP addresses;
		- Sorting of subnets;
		- SMTP auth;
		- subnet splitting;
		- API 
		- search for available subnets;
		- Show Subnet name instead of subnet IP address;
	
	- Optional
		- better exception handling (functions);
		- Overlapping subnets option in config files;
		- RDNS zone file export (in admin!);
		- IPv6 migration guide document;
		- Overlapping subnets if VRF is enabled;
	
	- Problematic
		- Subnet scan for alive IP addresses (ICMP);
		- ICMP check if IP is alive;
